# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  MinIO Phase 2 — CSV Import via MinIO
#  Phase 3 — Full Regression (Groups A + B + C + D combined)
#  Phase 4 — Cleanup verification (deprecated endpoints return 410)
#
#  VS Code REST Client extension required
#
#  PREREQUISITES:
#   1. docker compose up -d  (all services including MinIO)
#   2. node src/scripts/setup-minio.js  (buckets already created in Phase 0)
#   3. npm run start:event  AND  npm run start:guest  (or monolith)
#   4. DB migration already ran: filePath column renamed to fileKey
#   5. Fill in @ADMIN_TOKEN and @SHOW_ID below after AUTH-02
#
#  MinIO Console: http://localhost:9001
#  Login:         ticketbox_admin / ticketbox_secret_2026
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl     = http://localhost:3333
@minioUrl    = http://localhost:9000
@contentType = application/json

