#    [ ] B-05  Duplicate import returns 409 Conflict
#    [ ] B-06  Partial error CSV: 1 success, 1 error in errorDetails
#    [ ] B-07  Wrong file type: job FAILED or COMPLETED with all-error rows
#    [ ] B-08  MinIO offline: presigned URL endpoint returns 503
#    [ ] B-09  MinIO offline: worker marks job FAILED, worker keeps running
#    [ ] B-10  List jobs returns all jobs newest-first
#    [ ] B-11  Filter by showId returns only matching jobs
#
#  Group C (Regression):
#    [ ] C-01  Steps 1-4 wizard unaffected
#    [ ] C-02  Public event list — image_url is MinIO key, not /uploads/ path
#    [ ] C-03  Admin update event with MinIO key succeeds
#    [ ] C-04  Draft retrieval — MinIO key persisted in MongoDB
#
#  Group D (Infrastructure):
